* other features

- Before connecting, weex checks whether any local file
   is actually changed. Weex connects only when the remote
   site needs updating.

- Support for bidirectional transfer (It will be supported from Ver 3.0.0).

- Update the cache after each file transfer

- Man page update

- Check that weex 2.6.x debian patches are also in weex 3.0.0
